{"article_id":"GhcRr5jLljKWKvMH","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Michael Brown , the 18-year-old black man","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"whose fatal shooting by a white police officer in the St. Louis suburb of Ferguson in August touched off weeks of racially-charged rioting ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"had marijuana in his system ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"was initially shot at close range","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and does not appear to have been killed","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"while running away ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"according to experts","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"who reviewed the official autopsy and toxicology report .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"The documents ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"obtained by the St. Louis Post-Dispatch","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"and analyzed by two experts","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"not directly involved in the case ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"appears to contradict witness accounts","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that claimed","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Brown was running away from Police Officer Darren Wilson , 28 ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"when he was killed on Aug. 9 .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"The new information comes on the heels of reports","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that Wilson told authorities","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Brown had reached inside Wilson ' s police SUV","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and struggled for his gun ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"resulting in Wilson firing twice ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"hitting Brown once in the hand .","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Moments later and outside of the vehicle , Wilson fired the fatal bullets","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that sparked a national controversy .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"The newspaper had St. Louis medical examiner Dr. Michael Graham ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"who is not part of the official investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"review the autopsy report ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"and he determined","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that it \" does support","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that there was a significant altercation at the car \"","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"including a shot","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that hit Brown ' s right hand .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Dr. Judy Melinek , a forensic pathologist in San Francisco","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"who also reviewed the documents ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"concurred","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that the autopsy \" supports the fact","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that this guy is reaching for the gun ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and that it did not support claims","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Brown was shot","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"while running away from Wilson ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"or with his hands up .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"The toxicology test .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"also obtained by the newspaper","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"and performed by a St. Louis University laboratory ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"revealed marijuana in Brown ' s blood and urine .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Alfred Staubus , a consultant in forensic toxicology at The Ohio State University College of Pharmacy , told the newspaper","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"THC could impair judgment or slow reaction times","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"but that there was no reliable measurement","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to make those conclusions .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"\" The detection of THC in the postmortem blood of Michael Brown really indicates","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"his recent use of marijuana","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"( within a few hours )","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"and that he may or may not have been impaired at the time of his death , \"","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Staubus said .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"The shots","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"fired outside of the vehicle","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"hit Brown in the forehead , upper right arm and twice in the chest ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"Melinek said .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"The fatal shot to the top of Brown ' s head indicates","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"he was falling forward or in a lunging position toward the shooter ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"The fact","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"that a sixth shot hit his forearm","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"and traveled from the back of the arm to the inner arm","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"shows","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Brown ' s palms could not have been facing Wilson ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"as some witnesses have said ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Melinek said .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"The findings could be at odds with those of a private autopsy","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"arranged by Brown ' s family ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"conducted by former New York City Chief Medical Examiner Michael Baden","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"and made public Aug. 18 .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Baden said","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"none of Brown ' s wounds appeared to have been from shots","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"fired at close range ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"noting a lack of stippling , or pattern of tiny blood spatters .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"However , Graham told the Post-Dispatch ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"`` Sometimes when it ' s really close , such as within an inch or so ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"there is no stipple , just smoke . ''","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"A third autopsy has been ordered by federal officials as part of their investigation","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"into whether Brown 's civil rights were violated .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"Results of that one have not been revealed .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"The New York Times ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"citing government officials","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"briefed on the federal civil rights investigation into the matter","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"while the federal investigation was continuing ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"the evidence so far did not support civil rights charges against Wilson .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"The officials told the Times","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"the forensic evidence supported Wilson ' s version of events ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"which was that he was trying to leave his vehicle","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"when Brown pushed him back in","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and sparked the struggle for the gun .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Surveillance video from a nearby store allegedly showed the 6-foot , 4-inch Brown committing a strong-arm robbery minutes before the confrontation ,","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"stealing a box of cigars from a shopkeeper","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"who he pushed out of his way .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"The Post-Dispatch ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"citing sources close to the investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"reported","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"that Wilson claims","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"he saw Brown and his friend , Dorian Johnson , walking down the middle of the street","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"and told them to move to the sidewalk .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"When he noticed Brown","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"holding cigars in his hand ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Wilson said","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"he realized","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"the pair matched a radio alert about a the robbery moments earlier .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"Wilson claims","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"he put his vehicle in park ,","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"and tried to get out ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"but Brown slammed the door shut","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"and punched Wilson in the through the open window ,","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"sparking the struggle for the gun ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"the source told the paper .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"A grand jury has been hearing testimony in the case since Aug. 20 ,","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"but has not yet returned an indictment or a no-bill against Wilson .","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"If the police officer is not indicted ,","depth":4},{"id":117,"text":"supporters of Brown have vowed to resume demonstrations","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"that began immediately after the shooting","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"and became violent , with looting , arrests and the imposition of a curfew .","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"President Obama consoled Brown 's family in the immediate aftermath ,","depth":2},{"id":121,"text":"and U.S. Attorney General Eric Holder went to Ferguson","depth":3},{"id":122,"text":"and announced a separate federal investigation .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":245,"left":242,"right":244,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":236,"right":241,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":176,"right":235,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":176,"left":146,"right":175,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":130,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":125,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":127,"right":128,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":3,"right":126,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":137,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":133,"right":136,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":8,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":9,"right":131,"relat